snippet.title: GinsengKing
snippet.description:
You think you've tried everything? Well, you haven't tried ginseng yet?!

You think you've tried everything? Well, you haven't tried ginseng yet?!

1 year.. 2 years.. How old can you grow it?

Grow a mind blowing ginsengs!

Which ginseng are you gonig to get this time?

let's grow awesome ginseng to make bank!

Ultra blockbuster time killing hybrid game of puzzle and tamagotchi style farming ginseng. Godly game!!

Ginseng is the real deal!

Let's give it a try?
